and the less trouble you'll have.

852
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:53,610
Understand?

853
00:40:57,710 --> 00:40:58,360
Follow me.

854
00:41:10,150 --> 00:41:12,440
Did you find out where Pongsri went
after entering the country?

855
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:13,320
Not yet.

856
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:14,110
But

857
00:41:15,190 --> 00:41:17,190
the Immigration Office said

858
00:41:17,190 --> 00:41:18,440
there's an Officer Li

859
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:20,700
who is also looking into Pongsri Leekpa.

860
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:25,340
Find Officer Li's profile for me.

861
00:41:25,710 --> 00:41:27,040
Okay, I'll go right now.

862
00:41:29,930 --> 00:41:34,440
[The Dark Romance]

863
00:41:42,150 --> 00:41:44,060
Why isn't your dad back yet?

864
00:41:44,150 --> 00:41:45,940
The food is getting cold.

865
00:41:47,070 --> 00:41:48,670
How about I page him?

866
00:41:49,360 --> 00:41:51,160
How can he check it while riding?

867
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:53,500
You eat. You eat.

868
00:41:59,690 --> 00:42:00,620
I want some, too.

869
00:42:03,760 --> 00:42:05,370
You little foodie.

870
00:42:07,360 --> 00:42:08,510
All you know is eating.

871
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:09,170
It's my dad.

872
00:42:09,530 --> 00:42:10,590
It must be your dad.

873
00:42:12,150 --> 00:42:13,370
Hello, where are you?

874
00:42:13,630 --> 00:42:15,550
I... I am. Who's this?
